  "prompt": "I scored 570 in neet 2 . What would be my expected rank, in total from neet 1 & 2?",
  "response": "The expected rank for a score of 570 in NEET can vary each year based on several factors, including the overall performance of candidates, the difficulty level of the exam, and the number of candidates appearing for the exam. \n\nIn previous years, a score in the range of 570 typically placed candidates within the top 5,000 to 10,000 ranks. However, for the most accurate prediction, it would be best to refer to the official results and analysis released by the National Testing Agency (NTA) or consult resources that provide NEET rank prediction based on the latest data.\n\nIf you are looking for a more specific estimate, I recommend checking with recent data trends or official counseling sources relevant to your exam year.",
